    <description>This Record-Triggered Flow is used within the Product Management Tool (PMT) to automatically notify all distribution lists when a key milestone is reached.
It sends an email notification when a Milestone record is completed with either:
- SPC Final 
- Go Live

For SPC Final, the flow distinguishes between Creation and Modification types to send a tailored message.
For Go Live, a single standard notification is sent.
ESG (responsible.investment@carmignac.com) is included only if SFDR Category = 6, 8 or 9</description>
